bilingual.source: It took the national flag of China.
Every Monday we raise the flag there.
bilingual.target: 每周一我们在那里升旗。

bilingual.source: What is on the Canadian national flag?
Our first flag had a white elephant on it.
bilingual.target: 我们的第一面旗帜上有一只白色的大象。

bilingual.source: We raise the flag here every Monday morning.
bilingual.target: 我们每周一早上在这里升旗。

bilingual.source: Flapping like a giant flag, which I pretend is mine.
bilingual.target: 像一面巨大的旗帜一样飘动，我假装它是我的。

bilingual.source: The Galápagos Islands are a territory of Ecuador but have their own flag.
bilingual.target: 加拉帕戈斯群岛是厄瓜多尔的领土，但有自己的旗帜。

bilingual.source: We need a wooden pole to hang the flag.
bilingual.target: 我们需要一根木杆来挂旗。

bilingual.source: The racing flag is often a chequer pattern.
bilingual.target: 赛车旗通常是棋盘图案。

bilingual.source: The pirate flag featured a pair of crossed skulls.
bilingual.target: 海盗旗上有一对交叉的头骨。

list.abstract: Flag（フラグ），网络流行词，英文单词原意为旗帜，指不好的预兆或者不详的信号。 立flag是流行的网络词语，最开始立flag的意思是单纯的就为自己设定一个小目标方向，但是每次立flag之后就被现实打脸了，所以网络上说立flag有时候也是一种调侃。 游戏中flag决定或引发剧情发展的特性，后来被广泛引申到ACG作品中，指引发某一特定事件的原因；后来再进一步引申为某一特定事件发生前的征兆或标志。
FLAG原本是一个编程指令，常被运用于计算机语言，例如C语言或D语言中，常于用来记载变量的一个参数。后指在游戏或影视出现剧情分歧时做出的影响后续剧情发展的选择，源自于编程术语，英语中的原意是信号或旗帜。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, where's the flag? That's intentional grounding. Totally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么不掷黄旗，那绝对是故意出界。绝对的。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, please sit back, relax, and join us as we take our final lap as indicated by the waving of this racing flag.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总之，用放松的姿势，跟着我们一起跑完这最后一圈，就像这只赛车旗指示的一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Thanks to you and your Dr pepper, my teak end table upstairs looks like the Olympic flag. Think, Luke. Yes. Think, Luke.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是多谢你的乐倍汽水，我楼上的柚木桌现在看起来像奥运旗，用脑子，卢克。是的，用脑子，卢克。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm the king of the castles. Every castle needs a flag. Wow. They've got a flag. We don't need a silly flag.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是城堡的国王，每个城堡都需要一面旗子。怎么还有一面旗子。我们才不需要什么难看的旗子。

yingyinNormal.en: If only it had a flag. I've got a flag in my van if you'd like it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除非这里有一个旗子。如果你需要的话，我的货车里有旗子。

yingyinNormal.en: George, raise the flag. George, raise the flag. Peppa, ring the bell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，把旗子升起来。乔治，把旗子升起来。佩奇，敲响铃铛。

yingyinNormal.en: And I have flag knowledge that I have to get out of here!
yingyinNormal.zh: 而我满脑子的旗帜知识，我也得让它们赶紧出来。

yingyinNormal.en: Here is Granny pig. Hello, girls, can I get you anything. A flag, please. And it must be better than the boy's flag. I'll see what I can do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪奶奶来啦。你们好啊，需要点什么吗？一面旗子。我们的旗子肯定会比他们的好。让我来看看能做什么呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Sweet! Why are you waving a white flag? I'm surrendering to fun.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太棒了！你为什么挥白旗？因为太欢乐了，我投降了。

yingyinNormal.en: We don't want to talk to the boys. We don't want to talk to the girls. Granny pig has found a flag for the girl's den. This dress will make a pretty flag. Thank you, Granny.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不想和你们男孩说话。我们也不想和你们女孩说话。猪奶奶给女孩们的树屋找了一面旗子。这裙子能做一面漂亮的旗子。谢谢，奶奶。

yingyinNormal.en: We have a flag? Never fly it upside down. Unless the apartment's in distress.
yingyinNormal.zh: 咱还有旗子呢啊？千万别弄反了，除非公寓面临危机。

yingyinNormal.en: Before I sign off, I'd like to share with you all one last use for a white flag.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在节目正式停播前， 我想跟大家分享白旗的最后一个用处。

yingyinNormal.en: So, Sheldon says you have a new girlfriend. Yeah, which he rudely announced on my flag show.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿说你交了新的女朋友。对啊，他在我旗帜节目上无礼地宣布这消息。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, my little Flag-keteers, it looks like the last episode of Fun with Flags is at an end.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的小旗友们，最后一集《有趣的旗帜》就要结束了。

yingyinNormal.en: Roommate agreement, section 27, paragraph 5: The roommate agreement, like the American flag, cannot touch the ground.
yingyinNormal.zh: 室友协议第27章第5段写明：室友协议书与美国国旗一样，都不许落地。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's start by identifying the parts of our flag. This edge is the hoist, and it's used to... Excuse me, sorry, excuse me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们先开始认识旗帜的结构，这边是吊孔，用来……抱歉，借过一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Not really. We have a lot of turnover here. That flag outside has been at half-mast since April. That's why we have these.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也不行。这里经常有人去世。从四月以来，外面就一直在降半旗。所以才有这个。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, I'm sure you're thinking, "The final episode? who will stand between us and flag ignorance." I know I was thinking that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道你们一定在想，"居然最终集了是谁要害你们变成旗帜盲了"。像我就有这个想法。

yingyinNormal.en: I got no problem with wearing my uniform, saluting the flag and doing my duty. It's just carrying a gun and taking a human life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我穿制服没问题，向国旗行礼，尽我的义务。只是不可以拿枪杀人。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, that's television and movies. Section nine: miscellany. The apartment's flag is a gold lion rampant on a field of azure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，电视以及电影协议完成了。第九部分，杂项，公寓旗帜是一头在天蓝色背景下两腿站立的金色狮子。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 此外，他说，新泽西州教育部门在英语作业中已经发现至少有两篇文章显示出了学生有自杀的想法。
